way companies, government,

00:26:30.489 --> 00:26:31.530
lots of different things.

00:26:37.402 --> 00:26:39.360
PHILIP HOWARD: We have
to change the narrative.

00:26:39.360 --> 00:26:41.550
There needs to be a new way.

